### **Presenter Tips:**  
- **Engage:** Poll the audience on their tool usage (e.g., ‚ÄúWho uses ARM templates?‚Äù).  
- **Demo Prep:** Test scripts beforehand; use VS Code with ARM Tools extension .  
- **Trends:** Highlight Bicep adoption and multi-cloud strategies with Terraform .  

This structure balances technical depth with actionable insights, leveraging Azure‚Äôs native tools and best practices from the search results.
